{"tid":154141,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考完DSE千奇唔好亂做問卷同亂返暑期工","createTime":"2017-03-13T05:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T07:42:31.000Z","uid":29621,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c54223ab0b4471bff494ad0270aab697fc489816","tid":154141,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"Dse雞注意！考完試真係唔好隨便理門口班人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/153946/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/153946/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個Post我都想開返個講下經歷<br />\n<br />\n想當年我考DSE果陣 <br />\n<br />\n有同學話去返工做問卷有$5一份<br />\n<br />\n我心諗咁正就返下<br />\n<br />\n就係企係考場到做問卷攞資料<br />\n<br />\n之後打黎叫我返暑期工 <br />\n<br />\n間野叫國x書院 或者叫做 x力書院 <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多同行<br />\n<br />\n$50一個鐘 見幾吸引咪返下<br />\n<br />\n點知返工就係cold call去水人讀課程<br />\n<br />\nsell到一個學生我可以袋$3000<br />\n<br />\n返工有時會叫我地去上堂<br />\n<br />\n有時係英文 有時係D商科內容<br />\n<br />\n原來返工果班都係被sell對象黎<br />\n<br />\n聽過有條友sell左勁多朋友去讀 袋左唔少<br />\n<br />\n都有D係到返工既結果比人sell到比錢交學費<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 一個都無sell過 淨做問卷同打電話扮下野就算"},{"pid":"31001b454d0860ae1c8a2f09284bebb6b6ab877b","tid":154141,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9459ddd439b67deb41eff793b5b12d38c4431d69","tid":154141,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsosad無人理"},{"pid":"a6ad8e9e2d95c709a4759178d93a673512d54f93","tid":154141,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"仲有人佢地專請靚女 做 用黎吸毒撚"},{"pid":"140616d65490c258e80ea5ea6c5434ded53c7ff5","tid":154141,"uid":13816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e860086dfce3f5bfe81a50c05cac8